HEADWORD: Proto-Doric
<hw>Pro`to-Dor*ic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Proto-</ets> + <ets>Doric</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Arch.)</fld>
